-- Project Euler #31: Coin Sums
-- How many ways to make 200p using 1p,2p,5p,10p,20p,50p,100p,200p?
-- Answer: 73682

list 201 (0 give) repeat 0 1 set box 'ways let

[1 2 5 10 20 50 100 200] 'coins let

0 'ci let
(ci 8 lt)
(
  coins ci get 'coin let
  ways (
    'w let
    coin 'j let
    (j 200 le)
    (
      w j get w j coin sub get plus 'v let
      w j v set 'w let
      j 1 plus 'j let
    ) while
    w
  ) mutate 'ways let
  ci 1 plus 'ci let
) while

ways (200 get) lend swap free print
